    <x-sections.card-image-with-text
        image="/images/window-wall-floor-decals/top5pct-wall-decals-joliet.jpg"
        alt="Custom floor decals and floor graphics for retail businesses in Joliet Illinois"
        title="Advertising That Goes Where Customers Walk"
    >
        <p class="mb-4">Floor signs and floor decals put your brand message right in the path of your customers. Whether you are directing foot traffic through a retail store, marking social distancing guidelines in a waiting room, or creating a branded experience at a trade show or event, floor graphics get noticed because they occupy space that customers look at constantly, and they work best when they coordinate with matching <a href="/signs/business-signs/wall-signs" class="link-notification">wall signs</a> for a complete interior brand environment. We produce custom floor decals for businesses, event venues, gyms, schools, and organizations throughout Joliet, Shorewood, and Will and DuPage County, and many of our clients pair floor graphics with <a href="/signs/business-signs/window-signs" class="link-notification">window signs</a> to create a brand experience that flows from the exterior all the way through the interior of their space.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">We print floor graphics on heavy-duty non-slip vinyl with a matte laminate that provides traction underfoot and prevents slipping even in high-traffic areas. The laminate also protects the print from wear and scuffing so your floor graphic maintains its appearance through heavy use, and for permanent installations we use the same UV-rated inks we apply to our outdoor <a href="/signs/business-signs/banners" class="link-notification">banners</a> for colors that stay bold through extended exposure.</p>
        <p>All floor graphics from <a href="/" class="link-notification">Top 5 Percent</a> are printed with slip-resistant surface treatments that meet safety standards for commercial spaces. Coordinate floor graphics with <a href="/signs/business-signs/wall-signs" class="link-notification">wall signs</a> and <a href="/signs/business-signs/window-signs" class="link-notification">window signs</a> for a complete interior brand system. For trade show floors, pair floor graphics with branded <a href="/signs/table-signs/table-cloths" class="link-notification">table cloths</a> for a fully covered booth presentation. We serve businesses throughout Joliet, Plainfield, Romeoville, and the greater Chicagoland area. Call us at (815) 349 8600 to discuss your floor sign project today.</p>
    </x-sections.card-image-with-text>

    <x-sections.card-image-with-text
        image="/images/window-wall-floor-decals/top5pct-article-window-wall-signs.jpg"
        alt="Floor graphics and branded floor decals for events and retail stores in Joliet Illinois"
        title="From Trade Show Floors to Retail Aisles"
        imagePosition="right"
    >
        <p class="mb-4">Floor graphics are incredibly versatile and work effectively across a wide range of applications and environments. Retail stores use them to create seasonal promotions, highlight sale items, and guide shoppers through specific pathways, and those same retail clients often pair floor graphics with <a href="/signs/business-signs/window-signs" class="link-notification">window signs</a> to create a complete branded environment from the street to the checkout. Gyms, fitness studios, event venues, and trade show exhibitors also use them to define zones and create immersive branded spaces, and for events where you need branded staff uniforms to match our <a href="/custom-apparel" class="link-notification">custom apparel</a> shop produces shirts, hoodies, and hats right next door.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">We produce floor graphics in any size, from small tile-sized decals to large-format floor wraps that cover entire areas. Custom shapes are also available, circular, square, arrow-shaped, and die-cut-to-shape floor decals are all within our production capabilities, and our <a href="/design-services/logo-design" class="link-notification">design team</a> can build the layout from scratch if you bring us your brand colors and a direction. If you have a specific layout idea in mind, bring your concept to us and we will produce exactly what you are envisioning.</p>
        <p>Our floor graphics are produced with full UV-resistant color printing so your message is vibrant and legible from every angle. Trade show setups benefit most when <a href="/signs/business-signs/banners" class="link-notification">banners</a>, <a href="/signs/table-signs/table-runners" class="link-notification">table runners</a>, and floor graphics all carry the same brand design. Hand out <a href="/promotional-items" class="link-notification">promotional items</a>, mugs, tote bags, koozies, that reinforce the same messaging on your booth floor. We are a veteran owned shop in Joliet serving the full Will and DuPage County area and beyond. Call us at (815) 349 8600 or stop by 121 Springfield Avenue to discuss your floor graphic project.</p>
    </x-sections.card-image-with-text>

